The following steps are executed in sequence
Step 1: Spin up a Redis container.
Step 2: Spin up logstash Container with persistent Shipper configuration and logs. Link logstash container with Redis; Exposed ports should be mapped for demonstraion purpose
Step 3: Spin up Elastic Search container with persistent configuration and logs. Exposed ports should be mapped for demonstration purpose.
Step 4: Spin up logstash Container with persistent Collector Configuration and logs. Link Logstash container with Redis container. Link logtash container with Elastic Search container. Exposed ports are mapped (For demonstration purpose).
Step 5: Spin up Kibana Container with persistent configuration and logs. Exposed ports should be mapped.
